description: Nutrilicious . . .That's the word that we use to describe Hut-K's menu."Hut-K" is a modern colloquial Indian term that means "not the mainstream" or "different" and “Chaats” are savory Indian street food known for their multitudes of tastes and flavors in a single bite. In addition, chaat dish have a distinct feel or crunch to it. Together, the experience of taste, flavors and feel, we at Hut-K, would like to describe it as the “Party In Mouth”.
name: Hut-K
